= ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]\nhashMap.contains \"one\" = true\nhashMap.contains \"three\" = false\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.contains\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">contains</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L177-L190","name":"Batteries.HashMap.findEntry?","line":177,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.findEntry?","doc":"Given a key `a`, returns a key-value pair in the map whose key compares equal to `a`.\nNote that the returned key may not be identical to the input, if `==` ignores some part\nof the value.\n```\ndef hashMap := ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]\nhashMap.findEntry? \"one\" = some (\"one\", 1)\nhashMap.findEntry? \"three\" = none\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.findEntry?\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">findEntry?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> (<span class=\"fn\">α</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L174-L175","name":"Batteries.HashMap.instGetElemOptionTrue","line":174,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.instGetElemOptionTrue","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.instGetElemOptionTrue\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">instGetElemOptionTrue</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/GetElem.html#GetElem\">GetElem</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>) (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) =&gt; <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#True\">True</a></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L163-L172","name":"Batteries.HashMap.find!","line":163,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.find!","doc":"Looks up an element in the map with key `a`. Panics if the element is not found.\n```\ndef hashMap := ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]\nhashMap.find! \"one\" = 1\nhashMap.find! \"three\" => panic!\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.find!\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">find!</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">β</span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L153-L161","name":"Batteries.HashMap.findD","line":153,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.findD","doc":"Looks up an element in the map with key `a`. Returns `b₀` if the element is not found.\n```\ndef hashMap := ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]\nhashMap.findD \"one\" 0 = 1\nhashMap.findD \"three\" 0 = 0\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.findD\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">findD</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">b₀</span> : <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">β</span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L143-L151","name":"Batteries.HashMap.find?","line":143,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.find?","doc":"Looks up an element in the map with key `a`.\n```\ndef hashMap := ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]\nhashMap.find? \"one\" = some 1\nhashMap.find? \"three\" = none\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.find?\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">find?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L132-L141","name":"Batteries.HashMap.modify","line":132,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.modify","doc":"Performs an in-place edit of the value, ensuring that the value is used linearly.\nThe function `f` is passed the original key of the entry, along with the value in the map.\n```\n(ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]).modify \"one\" (fun _ v => v + 1) = {\"one\" => 2, \"two\" => 2}\n(ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]).modify \"three\" (fun _ v => v + 1) = {\"one\" => 1, \"two\" => 2}\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.modify\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">modify</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">β</span> → <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L122-L130","name":"Batteries.HashMap.erase","line":122,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.erase","doc":"Removes key `a` from the map. If it does not exist in the map, the map is returned unchanged.\n```\ndef hashMap := ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]\nhashMap.erase \"one\" = {\"two\" => 2}\nhashMap.erase \"three\" = {\"one\" => 1, \"two\" => 2}\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.erase\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">erase</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L109-L120","name":"Batteries.HashMap.insert'","line":109,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.insert'","doc":"Similar to `insert`, but also returns a boolean flag indicating whether an existing entry has been\nreplaced with `a => b`.\n```\ndef hashMap := ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]\nhashMap.insert' \"three\" 3 = ({\"one\" => 1, \"two\" => 2, \"three\" => 3}, false)\nhashMap.insert' \"two\" 0 = ({\"one\" => 1, \"two\" => 0}, true)\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.insert'\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">insert'</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L97-L107","name":"Batteries.HashMap.insert","line":97,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.insert","doc":"Inserts key-value pair `a, b` into the map.\nIf an element equal to `a` is already in the map, it is replaced by `b`.\n```\ndef hashMap := ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]\nhashMap.insert \"three\" 3 = {\"one\" => 1, \"two\" => 2, \"three\" => 3}\nhashMap.insert \"two\" 0 = {\"one\" => 1, \"two\" => 0}\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.insert\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">insert</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Hashable\">Hashable</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap\">HashMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/76408f09466811154e0e42329962de19f95d178b/Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.lean#L88-L95","name":"Batteries.HashMap.isEmpty","line":88,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.isEmpty","doc":"Is the map empty?\n```\n(empty : Batteries.HashMap Int Int).isEmpty = true\n(ofList [(\"one\", 1), (\"two\", 2)]).isEmpty = false\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Batteries.HashMap.isEmpty\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">HashMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">isEmpty</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span cl